[(1)](https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=50037.420) **Some SCAM reports concerning Bitcoin Fog, beware!**

**Bitcoin Fog** acts as a mixing service or an online wallet. This service operates only through [[tor]] anonymization network. Funds transferred to the Fog get mixed with other users' funds. When requested, funds are paid out in multiple randomized transactions to further anonymize the source of money.

